      "date": "2015-01-16 21:07:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/fba056da-9dc2-11e4-a5bc-5254006e85c2).  Ran 6 tests.  1 tests failed: sanity.",
