        "subject": "LU-5712 libcfs: merge libcfs.a into libcfsutil.a",
        "message": "LU-5712 libcfs: merge libcfs.a into libcfsutil.a\n\nlibcfs.a is only user-string.c so we merge it into\nlibcfsutil.a library. Also use libtool to build the\nstatic libraries so they can correctly link against\nother libraries like liblustreapi.so.\n\nChange-Id: I37d41cb78a0de6ef7eff976701f4df361c1a5d99\nSigned-off-by: James Simmons <uja.ornl@gmail.com>\n"
